Whale Wars: Viking Shores
Every year, the people of the Faroe Islands herd pilot whales to their shallow shores and kill them for their meat. Whale Wars: Viking Shores follows the Sea Shepherd Conservation Society as it sets sail to end this ancient tradition known as &quot;The Grind.&quot;




3)  Into the Fire 
